[01/11/2017 23:59:39] <font color="#ffff00">Sí.</font>
[01/11/2017 23:59:41] <font color="#ffff00">(TOSE)</font>
[01/11/2017 23:59:42] <font color="#ffff00">Lindh...</font>
[01/11/2017 23:59:44] <font color="#ffff00">Lindholm.</font>
